OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowery rain
OL,6,Fwill push northeast through the
OL,7,Fevening, this occasionally heavy and
OL,8,Fperhaps thundery at times. Clear
OL,9,Fspells and scattered showers for the
OL,10,Frest of the night.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,13,Fshowers in the morning, turning drier
OL,14,Fin the afternoon. Cloudier with some
OL,15,Frain in the late evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
