OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCloud
OL,6,Fand outbreaks of rain on Monday clear
OL,7,Fto sunny spells and showers. Rather
OL,8,Fcloudy Tuesday with occasionally heavy
OL,9,Frain or showers. Further showers or
OL,10,Flonger spells of rain Wednesday.
